Membership form

More than 35,000 performers have chosen to be associated with SPEDIDAM.

   Declaring a registration or collecting fees does not mean that you are
   associated with SPEDIDAM.
   Why become associated with SPEDIDAM? Optional declaration to limit the
   effect of accession

Adhere to SPEDIDAM in 5 steps

   Step 1  -  Complete the act of adhesion online

   Step 2  -  Complete the act of adhesion online
     * proof of your professional activity as a performer (a pay slip, a
       certificate of payment of holiday shows, ...)
     * evidence of your participation in a commercial recording or
       broadcast performance (SPEDIDAM meeting sheet with either the pay
       slip or registration contract, or the pocket and booklet with your
       name corresponding to the disc or video marketed)
     * a bank account statement from your bank
     * a recent passport photo
     * another document that you consider useful for the study of your
       file

   Step 3  -  If necessary fill out the optional contribution limitation
   form

   Step 4  -  Validate

   Step 5  -  You will receive a confirmation email
     * Attached your pre-filled certificate of membership in PDF format
     * Print and send to SPEDIDAM 2 copies of this pre-filled form of
       membership and the optional form if necessary, signed with a check
       16 € to the order of SPEDIDAM, corresponding to the amount of the
       share.

   Read the detailed membership details by referring to the following
   document:
   Read the full text of the membership criteria in PDF format

